Description: To verify that Change PIN can be done through USSD.
To verify that Set Pin request is successful if all the mandatory fields are filled with valid values
To verify that error is displayed if MSISDN is left empty.
To verify that error is displayed if invalid network code is entered.
To verify that error is displayed if invalid PIN is entered.
To verify that error is displayed if new pin and confirm pin are different.
To verify that error is displayed if invalid language code is entered.
To verify that error is displayed if new pin is same as old PIN.
